                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-07-01</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This is an excellent written book that I would definitely recommend to anyone interested in Network Security. The author has a very professional approach to security assessment and every chapter covers in detail ways to find out information about systems and their vulnerabilities. The final chapter walks through the process of creating a detailed report about an attack. One of the best security related books I have ever read.</span>
                  
              
